## 11. Common Patterns

### 11.1 Pagination

```typescript
const [result, refetch] = useGetInvitationsQuery({
  variables: {
    first: 20,
    after: cursor,
  },
})

const loadMore = () => {
  refetch({
    after: result.data?.invitations.pageInfo.endCursor,
  })
}
```

---

### 11.2 Polling (Auto-Refresh)

```typescript
const [result] = useGetInvitationQuery({
  variables: { eventId },
  requestPolicy: 'network-only',
  context: useMemo(
    () => ({
      pollInterval: 30000, // Refresh every 30 seconds
    }),
    []
  ),
})
```

